In South Africa only the {{ljcomm|user=whites}} could vote, own [[slaves | property]], [[hookers and blow]], or learn. When all of the blacks were forced to live and work together, there was a large [[AIDS]] epidemic, and [[Lulz|hilarity]] ensued.
==Notable Trolls==
However, as with any major [[Livejournal]] community or [[website]], Apartheid had its own set of dedicated trolls. However these [[troll]]s were generally [[unfunny]] and failed at setting about any change for [[At least 100 years | at least 50 years]].
===Oliver Tambo===
Oliver Tambo was the leader of the ANC (African National Congress) trolling organization, who were pretty much the [[GNAA]] of apartheid. Together with Nelson Mandela, Tambo (running under the pseudonym [[timecop]]) hosted a weekly podcast where they outlined their failed attempt at [[lulz]], like spray-painting [[Goatse]] all over the streets of Capetown. He was eventually found out, and [[mediacrat]] humbled him when he brought Tambo to [[e-court]], and banished him to the #zambia IRC channel, because South Africa was for [http://www.encyclopediadramatica.com/media/voicemail2.ogg rich people and beautiful people and people with perfect friends and people with perfect lives, James.]
===Nelson Mandela===
[[Image:Brown.jpg|thumb|Mugshot of Nelson Mandela.]]
Nelson Mandela trolled under the nickname [[l0de]]. His claim to fame was hosting the ANC podcast, as well as porting the popular game [[Last Measure]] into [[wigger | Afrikaans]]. After he trolled the whites in South Africa by replacing all of their copies of [[Harry Potter | The Half Blood Prince]] with the [[pain series]] and Goatse, Mandela was thrown in jail for at least 100 years. He was later released and [[Barack Obama|made president]] as part of a program of [[troll's remorse|national reconciliation]].
===Steve Biko===
A counter-troll who [[Malcolm X|thought Mandela was too soft]], Biko's goal was to overthrow apartheid at any cost. So he spammed South Africa with his [[moralfag]]gotry until the authorities said STFU and [[b&]] him for life. However, he snuck back in via proxies and hid out on #soweto, continuing to spam. This caused the [[The Man]] to rage and [[Kill it with fire|purify]] the entire channel; Biko honorably provided employment for local school children as [[sockpuppet]]s to be [[Banned IRL|banned]] in his place. Finally, like other [[Kimmo Alm|great spammers]], Biko was at last brought low and died as a result of his prison [[pro-ana|hunger strike]].
===Eugene Terreblanche===
Eugene Terreblanche (Terre Blanche, "White Earth" - [[lol|get it]]??), a [[Kim Jong Il|great revolutionary leader]] and [[redneck|reverse nigger]], was an Afrikaner farmer who sensibly did not support turning his country over to a pack of [[Bix nood|hooting]] monkeys. As a result he determined to champion a noble cause: he would restore South Africa to the white man's [[Holocaust|tender administration]]. The first step to this was the founding of the AW[[B]], a far-right militia with which he promptly invaded one of SA's many disease-ridden slums. After losing 90% of his army to immediate super-AIDS and having the remainder raped to death, Terreblanche then embarked on a notable career of [[buy a dog|setting dogs]] on uppity pump jockeys, tl;dr [[defamation]] trials, cringe-inducing [[Lemon Party|sex scandals]], going to [[Internet jail|jail]], falling off his horse, [[Libertarianism|failing politically]], and as a capper getting [[Guinea Pig|cut to pieces]] with a machete last Thursday.

==The End Of Apartheid==

<center><youtube>SiXNUaSjXRY</youtube></center>

When South Africa's head mod Pieter Willem Botha [[Banned IRL|had a stroke]] and [[deleting your livejournal|deleted his livejournal]], Desmond Tutu became the new leader. In an act of [[racism|reverse racism]], he decided to [[permaban]] all the whites, symbolically ending apartheid. However, the trolls have made a resurgence in the past few years, using the Jewish Media Conspiracy and [[GRIDS]] to disrupt the lives of black persons all across South Africa. Because of all the bloodshed, South Africans have not been able to attend as many [[Bantown#BBQ|BBQ]]s as they have funerals. There are now very few reported sightings of [[black]]s in South Africa, as they have all fled to the [[Habbo Hotel]], closing down pools due to AIDS and [[stingray]]s. South Africa is still, however, the [[babyfuck]] [http://www.iol.co.za/index.php?art_id=vn20100301081655212C583935 capital] [http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/1703595.stm of] [http://www.thebody.com/content/whatis/art20708.html Planet] [http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/africa/south-africa-shocked-as-six-charged-with-raping-baby-girl-616747.html Earth;] this quite makes up for the [[abortion]] of lulz caused by apartheid's abolition.

It is very sad to see apartheid's end, as it generated many LULZ. Fortunately, the world still has [[Israel]] around to take up South Africa's mantle: pwning [[Palestine|lesser races]] with [[American]] ordnance, building [[Objectophilia#Objectophile_Examples|sexy segregation walls]] for great justice, and blackmailing [[Iran|the region]] with [[My Tiny Dick|hidden nukes]]. They also, like white South Africa, totally ignore unfavorable [[United Nations|UN]] resolutions and [[pretty cool guy|doesn't afraid of anything]].

